testsuite.name: com.aninfo.integration.cucumber.CucumberTest

testcase.name: Given No tickets to access
When Trying to get tickets
Then I get no tickets
Given Two tickets
When Trying to get tickets
Then I get two tickets
Given Ticket with name Ticket1 because of accesing
When Trying to find ticket with name Ticket1
Then I get the ticket appropriately
Given Ticket with name MyTicket1 because of accesing
When Trying to find ticket with name MyTicket2
Then I get an Invalid Ticket Exception because of accessing
Given No ticket with name ticket1
When Trying to create a ticket with name ticket1
Then It is created successfully
And Ticket is named ticket1
Given A ticket with status NOT STARTED
When Trying to edit the status from NOT STARTED to IN PROGRESS
Then Status is edited successfully
Given A ticket with severity S1
When Trying to edit the severity from S1 to S2
Then Severity is edited successfully
Given A ticket with priority LOW
When Trying to edit the priority from LOW to HIGH
Then Priority is edited successfully
Given A ticket with an empty info
When Trying to edit the info to a different one
Then Info is edited successfully
Given A ticket with name ticket1
When Trying to edit the name from ticket1 to ticket2
Then Name is edited successfully
Given Two tickets with names ticket1 and ticket2
When Trying to edit the name of ticket1 to the same name of ticket2
Then I get a Ticket Name Already Taken Exception
And It remain with the original name
Given A ticket
When Searching this ticket by it's code
Then It is found successfully
And The ticket's code matches
Given no tickets to search
When Searching this ticket by it's code
Then I get an Invalid Ticket Exception because of searching
